tag_line: add Boost By Gear to every vehicle!
title: [MultiSlot Plugin] Boost By Gear for every vehicle
message:
[B]This is a plugin for the MultiSlot /  General Modslot Generator, download this first for this to work:[/B]
[URL]https://www.beamng.com/resources/general-modslot-generator-multimod.31265/[/URL]
When selected in the MultiSlot Base, this plugin adds Boost By Gear functionality to every vehicle ingame. You can customize each gears wastegate pressure in the Tuning tab:
[ATTACH]1143701[/ATTACH]

You do need to have a Turbo on the vehicle for that!
via: packed by repo on Thu, 20 Jun 2024 01:01:18 GMT
